all, his theater was taken from life as his life was theatrical., awards=2 wins & 4 nominations., lastupdated=2015-09-02 00:42:30.710000000, type=movie, languages=[French], directors=[Ariane Mnouchkine], writers=[Ariane Mnouchkine], imdb=Document{{rating=7.4, votes=498, id=77941}}, countries=[France, Italy], genres=[Biography, Drama, History], tomatoes=Document{{viewer=Document{{rating=4.2, numReviews=392, meter=93}}, production=New Yorker Films, lastUpdated=Mon Aug 17 21:04:04 CEST 2015}}, num_mflix_comments=1}}
