 train station. This hero, after the war, was completely forgotten, and his story comes out just in the 1980s because some of the Hungarian Jews wanted to meet him again., awards=5 wins., lastupdated=2015-08-31 03:46:11.937000000, type=movie, languages=[Italian], directors=[Alberto Negrin], writers=[Enrico Deaglio (novel), Sandro Petraglia, Stefano Rulli], imdb=Document{{rating=7.2, votes=384, id=278017}}, countries=[Italy, France, Sweden, Hungary], genres=[Biography, Drama, History], tomatoes=Document{{viewer=Document{{rating=3.5, numReviews=290, meter=62}}, rotten=3, lastUpdated=Fri Jul 24 20:59:26 CEST 2015, critic=Document{{rating=5.5, numReviews=7, meter=57}}, production=Castle Hill Productions, fresh=4}}}}
